### Next.js Specifics

- Uses **App Router** (`app/` directory) by default
- Server Components are the default — use `'use client'` for client-side interactivity
- Route handlers in `app/api/` for backend endpoints
- `getServerSideProps`/`getStaticProps` are legacy — use Server Components or `generateStaticParams` instead
- Image optimization via `next/image`
